    <item>
      <title>也门海岸附近最近的船只袭击中船只被击中并受损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/ship-hit-and-damaged-in-latest-vessel-attack-near-yemen-s-coast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚丁湾一艘商船遭到导弹袭击，造成人员死亡，这是自胡塞武装分子在世界上最繁忙的海上航道之一对商船发起一波袭击以来，首次确认船员死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/ship-hit-and-damaged-in-latest-vessel-attack-near-yemen-s-coast</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 13:39:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔重申美联储需要对通胀更有信心才能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/powell-reiterates-fed-needs-more-confidence-on-inflation-to-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔向立法者重申，在政策制定者确信他们已经赢得了对抗通胀的战斗之前，美联储并不急于降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/powell-reiterates-fed-needs-more-confidence-on-inflation-to-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约央行重燃地区银行担忧，国债延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/treasuries-fall-ahead-of-powell-s-remarks-and-us-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债市场周三上涨，收益率跌至几周来的最低水平，纽约社区银行(New York Community Bancorp)股价的最新暴跌再次引发了人们对美国地区银行健康状况的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/treasuries-fall-ahead-of-powell-s-remarks-and-us-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 09:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔坚持脚本，股市上涨； NYCB 下跌：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街交易员松了一口气，杰罗姆·鲍威尔再次表示，虽然强劲的经济将使官员们暂时按兵不动，但他预计美联储今年将降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 22:46:54 GMT</pubDate>
